data.description: **Seller will be $10K towards your RATE buy down** Welcome to the Gates Estate, one of Ardmore Oklahoma's first Luxury homes! This property was built in the early 1900's by the late Frank S Gates, who was also a founding member of the Ardmore Rotary Club and community leader. This home has long been one of the treasured beauties in South West Ardmore,Ok. Sitting on a gorgeous half acre lot( with front & back sprinklers), this property boasts over 4,000 SQ ft of living space including a garage apartment(with it's own address)! Just inside the front door you have an updated half bath and staircase leading up to the massive 3/4 bedroom options. Downstairs you will enjoy a large entertainment space with a charming fireplace, built-ins for book storage, all original hard wood flooring throughout and original pocket doors keep the history rich in this home. The kitchen is a dream come true with amazing storage, Corian Countertops, center island with a GAS range, and huge walk in pantry with automatic lighting and amazing laundry room!! GUYS- You are never going to leave this bedroom that includes an amazing Parlor/TV Room/Library(Tv included) and a huge bathroom with fierce cheetah print walls, it makes this the perfect retreat after a long day of work! If that downs make you happy, the HUGE backyard and covered porch surely will! This is an amazing opportunity to buy a piece of Ardmore history and the garage apartment could help generate extra income! Don't miss this one- Call today to schedule your showing NOW!
